description:
Context
- I am originally from Shanghai in China, so I am pretty critical and meanwhile trustworthy regarding this review;

Why 4 stars
- 上海生煎包 Shanghai-Style Pan-Fried Pork Buns are so good! Pretty close to what I had in Shanghai;
- 上海南翔小笼包 Shanghai-Style Steamed Pork Dumplings are good too. The wrappers are thin enough;

Why not 5 stars
- Other dishes are average;

Side notes
- The followings are well made:
     - 葱油饼 Green Onion Pancake ;
- The followings are not that good from a Shanghai local's perspective:
     - 上海炒年糕 Shanghai-Style Stir-Fried Rice Cakes - my westerner friend thinks it is great;
     - 上海春卷(素) Shanghai-Style Spring Rolls (Vegetarian) 
     - 锅贴 Pan-Fried Pot Stickers;
     - 炸酱面 Beijing-Style Noodle in Black Bean Sauce;
     - 榨菜肉丝汤面 Pork with Sichuan Pickled Mustard Noodle Soup;
